teleportToY = 3089;
}

teleportToY = 3210;
}

So i added this-
if (command.startsWith(“tar”)) {
teleportToX = 2884;
teleportToY = 9799;
}

so it now looks like this-

if (command.startsWith(“gopk”)) {
teleportToX = 3244;
teleportToY = 3517;
}
if (command.startsWith(“cw”)) {
teleportToX = 2440;
teleportToY = 3089;
}
if (command.startsWith(“kbd”)) {
teleportToX = 3341;
teleportToY = 3210;
}
if (command.startsWith(“tar”)) {
